{"tid":1281300,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[未來紅衛兵入] 爹親娘親不及毛主席親","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T13:47:38.000Z","uid":190579,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72b3efd2ef7d76807ace820575ee2a8981d1126a","tid":1281300,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派</div></span></span></span><br />\n，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派，<span style=\"color: red;\">群眾鬥群眾，要你自相殘殺</span>，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟，共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持清醒，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易上五毛當<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒呀各位！小心玩膠自焚！</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n(突發)香港紅衛兵第一小隊，成式招收隊員！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ddyGLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ddyGLS</a>"},{"pid":"d198d3c11cfc3bf22e9f9dbd9db6c0d5e9fc2a20","tid":1281300,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02fa390cae773487aeb74a866d15d0b1acf65af4","tid":1281300,"uid":258115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"支持共產黨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbeeae30d6ddbec82060bb725193a448a80c865","tid":1281300,"uid":262032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99805498074fc577537dcaa89a0c01f9d00b168b","tid":1281300,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"寶寶好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"